The paper deals with the problem of online identification of time-varying systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also uses Bayesian inference and regularization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with the estimation of hyper-parameters and the use of a forgetting factor, which are topics that fall under the categories of statistics (cs.ST) and information theory (cs.IT).
